Sure, I can help you troubleshoot the MFA (BSA) setup for your Mikrotik VPN.

I understand you have configured your Mikrotik device correctly, and your Java-based BSA (Bilateral Simple Authenticator) module should be working seamlessly with the FreeRADIUS module setup. However, it seems there's some confusion in the `post-auth` block related to when and how to perform the BSA (MFA) authentication alongside LDAP.

